# AgentsArena

AgentsArena is a Python 3.11 library for pure, turn-based game simulation.

The current implementation focus is the simulation package only:
- sequential games
- deterministic games
- perfect-information games

Phase 0 bootstraps the repository layout, packaging, and baseline tooling.
